item.title: WPA Highjacking (For Educational Purposes Only)
item.description: In this post im going to be exploring and illustrating the process of WPA hijacking Getting Started Before embarking on our journey into the fascinating world of WPA hijacking, there are a few crucial prerequisites to consider. Depending on your preferred setup, you can either install Linux or set up a virtual machine (VM). Although we recommend Kali Linux for the best experience, it’s not mandatory. Installing Linux If you choose to install Linux, we suggest using Kali Linux 2023.
